contentrichtext.text: '''Zhu''' or '''ZHU''' may refer to: *[[Zhu (surname)]], common Chinese surnames :*[[Zhu Yuanzhang]], first emperor of the Ming Dynasty *[[Zhu River]], or Pearl River, in southern China *[[Zhu (state)]], ancient Chinese state, later renamed Zou. *[[Zhu (string instrument)]], ancient Chinese string instrument *[[Zhu (percussion instrument)]], ancient Chinese percussion instrument *[[Zhuhai Sanzao Airport]] - ZHU is the 3 letter IATA code for the airport *[[Zhu languages]] *[[Houston Air Route Traffic Control Center]], known as ZHU {{disambig}}
